Alex Baretta wrote:
> use the Reply-all button

I hope not!

I read this list (and many others) through Gmane gateway.

Espacially to get rid of thousands of emails that bloated my mailbox.
Answering with "Reply-all" will send one email to the list _and_ one to
the previous sender.
The To-list one will go through Gmane's, but but the other one will go
to the mail Inbox. Subscribing through Gmane was about to avoid
receiving emails, so, take care of that...

What should be done is to care of where your email is sent to. That the
basics of talking/discussing. People cant assume having constructive
discussion if he just throw the answer and let it goes where it goes. So
what I would say is just "check who your message is sent to, that's fair".

Cheers.

